Quick Install Instructions
==========================
1. Generate configure file
# Run following commands under project top dir
$ ./autogen.sh

2. Configure (on different platforms)
2.1 Titan - Cray XK7
$ ./configure CC=cc FC=ftn --with-gni-cookie=0x5420000 --with-gni-ptag=250

2.2 Sith - IB cluster
$ ./configure CC=mpicc FC=mpif90

2.3 BlueGene/P
$ ./configure CC=/bgsys/drivers/ppcfloor/comm/default/bin/mpixlc FC=/bgsys/drivers/ppcfloor/comm/default/bin/mpif90 CFLAGS="-g -O0 -qarch=450 -qtune=450" --with-dcmf="/bgsys/drivers/ppcfloor"

2.4 Kraken - Cray XT5
$ ./configure CC=cc FC=ftn

3. Compile
# Under project top dir
$ make
